      <title>高盛的卡鲁伊：已经出台了很多宽松政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-06/a-lot-of-easing-has-been-delivered-goldman-sachs-karoui</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛首席信贷策略师 Lotfi Karoui 表示，资本市场已经实施了许多宽松政策，而 Richard Bernstein Advisors 固定收益总监 Michael Contopoulos 则表示，我们不应该买入高风险债券。他们就“彭博实际收益率”与 Sonali Basak 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-06/a-lot-of-easing-has-been-delivered-goldman-sachs-karoui</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 19:19:33 GMT</pubDate>
